      "id": "PopularPost266411",
      "post_content": "Like so many have said before, the only thing wrong with this as it has already been done and done better. what it needed was to cost {R}{R} and return {R}{R}{R}{R} since in most cases people are only using red mana to pay for this anyway. Or we could have made it a Tribal Instant - Elemental and comboed it with [Brighthearth Banneret](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brighthearth Banneret) thus removing the 1 colorless mana in the cost and making it a (situational) Dark Ritual in red. But that might imply that it should have been printed in Lowyn or Morningtide. Or they could have added a clause at the end saying that if you control 2 or fewer lands then it costs {R} rather than {R} + 1 other.  \n  \nI mean no offense to those in the team that thought this was a good idea, but it could have been done so much better.",
      "posted_by": "Kos4evr",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost266411\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Like so many have said before, the only thing wrong with this as it has already been done and done better. what it needed was to cost {R}{R} and return {R}{R}{R}{R} since in most cases people are only using red mana to pay for this anyway. Or we could have made it a Tribal Instant - Elemental and comboed it with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brighthearth Banneret\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brighthearth Banneret\">Brighthearth Banneret</a> thus removing the 1 colorless mana in the cost and making it a (situational) Dark Ritual in red. But that might imply that it should have been printed in Lowyn or Morningtide. Or they could have added a clause at the end saying that if you control 2 or fewer lands then it costs {R} rather than {R} + 1 other.<br/><br/>I mean no offense to those in the team that thought this was a good idea, but it could have been done so much better.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '266411'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy74883\">Kos4evr</span>\r\n                                (9/5/2012 9:11:58 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel